{"type": "article", "id": 20161, "title": "户外椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-04T07:40:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606001741Bf1sIPeXymG39Dhw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一把不锈钢做的户外椅子，设计师想将优雅也带到户外去。竖条状的不锈钢环绕着组成了靠背和扶手，它们在座位面交叉成网格状，显得简单而优雅。两边的转折处有两个三角形的镂空，用来缓解转角，也突出了横条与竖条的交叉感。但如果不是从正面俯瞰，椅子侧面的不锈钢竖条都是有重叠和交叉的，呈现出不同稀疏的网格纹路，也有深浅的变化。<a href=\"http://arnaud-lapierre.com/post/116386906386/strie-2015-outdoor-indoor-chair-stainless\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150401i5cLzprQuJWjhTwY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261504016FAf1qVLyoOYEpdJ.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261504025tKEryoCNF1Gx2Tf.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"353\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150403FNrzKjaWGU4tJyS2.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"631\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.631\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}